{"tid":2400663,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"移民講到底都係為自己著想，但係又有幾多人夠膽承認呢個事實？","createTime":"2021-02-09T06:44:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-09T11:08:47.000Z","uid":219007,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c73111109675dacb44e9f82d8883663d36413c24","tid":2400663,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T06:44:24.000Z","msg":"移民係絕對正確嘅選擇，我認為走對個人來講係最着數。但係我最睇唔過眼嘅就係，有啲人又要走但係又要扮撚晒野。唔該謙卑啲、誠實啲面對自己。<br />\n<br />\n你哋好多人因為 唔敢反抗/反抗唔到 條氣好唔順，而潛意識都知道係時候要為自己着想吓。 但係情緒上又覺得自己好自私於是乎產生好大罪惡感，跟住就將移民離開行為包裝成為抗爭，俾個藉口自己好過啲，<span class=\"red\"><strong>最大獲係連自己都呃埋</strong></span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n見啲人一路話「我哋香港人好撚堅」乜乜柒柒，但係同一時間撳緊機票執行李，其實真係好撚核突屌你老尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n 其實你知道你自己講緊大話，只不過唔敢承認。走咗去其他地方生活自然就會顧自己多啲，有啲人直情唔會再嚟香港嘅事。呢個係非常之自然同正常嘅事，唔明點解有人唔敢承認。<br />\n<br />\n做人最緊要謙卑啲，倒不如承認自己能力不大，改變唔到社會。唔好講到自己咁有用去掩飾自己內心嘅虛怯。你今日有得離開係有班細路攞條命換返嚟，<span class=\"red\">你想對得住佢哋就唔該珍惜你出國之後嘅生活。你下下扮撚晒野而最終都係為自己其實係仲更加對佢哋唔住。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n每個人做嘢最終都係為自己而負責，承認移民就係為自己其實又有咩問題呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 誠實啲面對自己吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"274728882a28b4d250afbbde8f9e3b5e880c3704","tid":2400663,"uid":146030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T06:46:26.000Z","msg":"走係為自己<br />\n抗爭絕對唔會係first priority"},{"pid":"aa1d52bd971580328bfa46b96ddd1becee7aad82","tid":2400663,"uid":33508,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T06:51:10.000Z","msg":"留低嘅咪一樣呃梗自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只要一日心底仲肯呃自己<br />\n就一日唔會放棄抗爭"},{"pid":"61b411b3f88022b0456b27440d8811b3b79e4451","tid":2400663,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T06:51:33.000Z","msg":"啱，大家做港豬就最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n［改變心態］香港變成點唔重要，最緊要自己活得開心就足夠！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2368342\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2368342</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後作為連下sir 信徒<br />\n幫手推廣下佢嘅概念<br />\n俾連登班黑暴知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聖誕節，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2329311/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2329311/page/1</a><br />\n肥佬黎俾人告國安法，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2323506/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2323506/page/1</a><br />\n中大畢業遊行，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2315353/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2315353/page/1</a><br />\n拜登贏咗，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2276817/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2276817/page/1</a><br />\n就黎國安法實行，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2184746/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2184746/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2073990/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2073990/page/1</a><br />\n612一周年，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2046361/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2046361/page/1</a><br />\n有武肺，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1850160/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1850160/page/1</a><br />\nPoly 打完，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1768364/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1768364/page/1</a><br />\n要選區議會，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1681018/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1681018/page/1</a><br />\n機場壓力測試完，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1548844/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1548844/page/1</a><br />\n8月大罷工完，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1417635/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1417635/page/1</a><br />\n728元朗遊行完，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1383029/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1383029/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"ccb8b45c3f791b9c0f563729dc907e929de5384e","tid":2400663,"uid":114275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T08:08:01.000Z","msg":"我移咗民仲洗唔洗交稅俾港共 ?"},{"pid":"625182e807ff825f79f64c74a75df986ffc91b00","tid":2400663,"uid":114193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T11:08:47.000Z","msg":"連下sir 又有每日一篇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}